    "name": "UGG",
    "profile": "UGG is down south music that's too real for mainstream. UGG is an underground rapper that definitely brings music to life. His sound, his lyrics, and just his very essence have made many ask why this artist isn’t signed to a major label. To be honest the mainstream would never fall in love with his music like the underground scene. His music captures your hearts and your minds as well as your soul. So if you are not afraid of real music, take a listen. You won't find any booty shaking party all night music hear just straight underground fire. UGG is from Dallas, TX where he was born and raised.\r\n\r\nUGG is an acronym for Under Ground Gangster.",
